# Class: obo:GENEPIO_0002098 (obsolete: wild type (WT))

AnnotationAssertion(obo:IAO_0000115 obo:GENEPIO_0002098 "A wild type (WT) resistance phenotype indicates a bacterial pathogen belongs to a \"Naïve\", susceptible wild-type population with respect to a given antimicrobial. No acquired or mutational resistance mechanisms are
